N:video-production
D:Programmable video production with Remotion. Generate automated, brand-consistent videos at scale from text instructions using scene planning, asset orchestration, and validation gates.
G:video remotion animation storytelling automation react

U[4]:
  Automated video generation — auto-generate videos from text instructions
  High-volume brand video production — produce in bulk with consistent style
  Marketing content — product intros, onboarding, promo videos
  Programmable content — integrate narration·visuals·animation
S[5]{n,action,details}:
  1,Video Spec,define audience·goal·duration(30s/60s/90s)·aspect_ratio(16:9/1:1/9:16)·tone·voice
  2,Scene Plan,structure each scene — specify Visual·Audio·Text·Transition·Duration
  3,Prepare Assets,checklist for logos(SVG)·screenshots(normalized)·audio(MP3·volume normalized)·fonts(woff2)
  4,Implement Remotion,compose <Composition> component; animate with interpolate; layer with AbsoluteFill
  5,Render & QA,npx remotion preview → verify timing/audio sync/text readability/transitions → final render
R[5]:
  Limit each scene to a clear 5-10 seconds
  Define and apply a consistent typography scale
  Align narration cues with visuals (audio sync)
  Ensure edge safe zones for mobile aspect ratios (9:16)
  Always run preview QA before final render
